[
    {
        "text": "We’ve eradicated measles.",
        "start": 1.635,
        "duration": 1.365
    },
    {
        "text": "Hurray!",
        "start": 3.0,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, no!",
        "start": 6.515,
        "duration": 1.025
    },
    {
        "text": "Now there’s no way\nI’ll go viral.",
        "start": 7.54,
        "duration": 2.67
    },
    {
        "text": "Cheer up, Measles.",
        "start": 10.21,
        "duration": 1.34
    },
    {
        "text": "No vaccine can hold you down.",
        "start": 11.55,
        "duration": 2.09
    },
    {
        "text": "But everyone will\ntake the vaccine",
        "start": 13.64,
        "duration": 1.78
    },
    {
        "text": "and we’ll be locked\nup in here forever.",
        "start": 15.42,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "Not everyone will\ntake the vaccine.",
        "start": 17.55,
        "duration": 2.145
    },
    {
        "text": "But, Polio, who wouldn’t want\nto protect their kids from us",
        "start": 19.695,
        "duration": 3.225
    },
    {
        "text": "using the most\nstudied, understood",
        "start": 22.92,
        "duration": 1.58
    },
    {
        "text": "and effective medical\nadvancements ever",
        "start": 24.5,
        "duration": 1.81
    },
    {
        "text": "achieved in human history?",
        "start": 26.31,
        "duration": 2.565
    },
    {
        "text": "You’d be surprised, Measles.",
        "start": 28.875,
        "duration": 1.725
    },
    {
        "text": "The human brain’s got a\nlot of tricks that make",
        "start": 30.6,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "bad ideas seem reasonable.",
        "start": 32.82,
        "duration": 2.11
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, let me show you.",
        "start": 34.93,
        "duration": 1.925
    },
    {
        "text": "Vaccines are dangerous.",
        "start": 36.855,
        "duration": 1.575
    },
    {
        "text": "My sister’s kids\ngot sick every time",
        "start": 38.43,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "they got a vaccine.",
        "start": 40.47,
        "duration": 1.35
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, I know that one.",
        "start": 41.82,
        "duration": 1.29
    },
    {
        "text": "That’s called an anecdote.",
        "start": 43.11,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "That’s right, Measles.",
        "start": 44.88,
        "duration": 1.23
    },
    {
        "text": "People love stories that\nconfirm their suspicions,",
        "start": 46.11,
        "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
        "text": "and they can’t help\nbut remember that story",
        "start": 48.86,
        "duration": 2.23
    },
    {
        "text": "instead of the\nmany other stories",
        "start": 51.09,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "with a different\nending, because humans",
        "start": 53.01,
        "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
        "text": "can’t escape something\ncalled \"confirmation bias.\"",
        "start": 55.29,
        "duration": 2.9
    },
    {
        "text": "And it works like this.",
        "start": 58.19,
        "duration": 1.48
    },
    {
        "text": "This one commuter — \nhe can’t help but miss",
        "start": 59.67,
        "duration": 3.45
    },
    {
        "text": "the train.",
        "start": 63.12,
        "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
        "text": "He’s sure he loses\nand he’s never won —",
        "start": 65.14,
        "duration": 3.602
    },
    {
        "text": "Every time.",
        "start": 68.742,
        "duration": 1.188
    },
    {
        "text": "Even though it’s 50/50\nwhen he’s gotten through.",
        "start": 69.93,
        "duration": 5.27
    },
    {
        "text": "The story in his mind\nis said and done, yeah.",
        "start": 75.2,
        "duration": 5.21
    },
    {
        "text": "He tends to count the hits\nand dismiss the misses.",
        "start": 80.41,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "A picture forms in his mind.",
        "start": 82.75,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "It fits the frame but the\nframer is suspicious,",
        "start": 85.48,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "so caught up in his grind.",
        "start": 87.91,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s natural for\nthe brain to not",
        "start": 90.47,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "clock the moment he got\nto work on time with ease.",
        "start": 92.0,
        "duration": 3.59
    },
    {
        "text": "He can’t recall the\ndata that doesn’t fit.",
        "start": 95.59,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "He sees what he wants to see.",
        "start": 97.99,
        "duration": 1.757
    },
    {
        "text": "But scientists have\nbeen wrong so many times.",
        "start": 99.747,
        "duration": 2.953
    },
    {
        "text": "And they can’t even\nbe 100 percent certain.",
        "start": 102.7,
        "duration": 2.67
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s all just a theory.",
        "start": 105.37,
        "duration": 1.605
    },
    {
        "text": "They call that the\n\"perfectionist fallacy,\"",
        "start": 106.975,
        "duration": 2.385
    },
    {
        "text": "where people think that\nwithout complete certainty,",
        "start": 109.36,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "all assumptions are equal.",
        "start": 111.82,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "And boy,\nis that wrong.",
        "start": 113.2,
        "duration": 3.45
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, it’s true there\nused to be phrenology.",
        "start": 116.65,
        "duration": 4.2
    },
    {
        "text": "And remember alchemy was hip.",
        "start": 120.85,
        "duration": 5.772
    },
    {
        "text": "Eggs were good, then bad,\nthen good, then bad for you.",
        "start": 126.622,
        "duration": 4.74
    },
    {
        "text": "Don’t know what’s what.",
        "start": 131.362,
        "duration": 1.422
    },
    {
        "text": "The facts, they seem to flip.",
        "start": 132.784,
        "duration": 2.306
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah!",
        "start": 135.09,
        "duration": 1.025
    },
    {
        "text": "Darn it.",
        "start": 136.115,
        "duration": 1.275
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes, it’s a theory, but so\nis light, gravity, space",
        "start": 137.39,
        "duration": 3.27
    },
    {
        "text": "and time.",
        "start": 140.66,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "Evidence and experiments work\nto prove it and blow your mind.",
        "start": 142.32,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s hard to comprehend that\nscience might write a song",
        "start": 147.32,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "and then change the key.",
        "start": 150.2,
        "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s a method to learn,\nnot just be right.",
        "start": 152.22,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "They see what\nthey want to see.",
        "start": 154.55,
        "duration": 3.027
    },
    {
        "text": "But it’s undeniable that as they",
        "start": 157.577,
        "duration": 1.833
    },
    {
        "text": "increased the\nvaccine scheduling,",
        "start": 159.41,
        "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
        "text": "autism diagnoses skyrocketed.",
        "start": 161.15,
        "duration": 2.325
    },
    {
        "text": "That logical fallacy is\ncalled \"confusing correlation",
        "start": 163.475,
        "duration": 2.655
    },
    {
        "text": "with causation.\"",
        "start": 166.13,
        "duration": 1.11
    },
    {
        "text": "And humans do it\nall the time.",
        "start": 167.24,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "When summer’s\nburning, ice cream sales —",
        "start": 170.78,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": "they go sky-high.",
        "start": 173.3,
        "duration": 2.68
    },
    {
        "text": "Right beside it goes\nthe murder rate.",
        "start": 175.98,
        "duration": 3.355
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah.",
        "start": 179.335,
        "duration": 1.365
    },
    {
        "text": "We might conclude that\nfrozen treats lead us to die,",
        "start": 180.7,
        "duration": 5.23
    },
    {
        "text": "but that’s not true.",
        "start": 185.93,
        "duration": 1.14
    },
    {
        "text": "They really just relate.",
        "start": 187.07,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah!",
        "start": 188.96,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "The human mind is\ncompromised when",
        "start": 191.09,
        "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
        "text": "swayed by emotional weight.",
        "start": 193.67,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "When you’re a\npattern-seeking primate,",
        "start": 196.27,
        "duration": 2.595
    },
    {
        "text": "it’s second nature\nto conflate.",
        "start": 198.865,
        "duration": 1.94
    },
    {
        "text": "The data is so\nclose that it seems",
        "start": 200.805,
        "duration": 2.105
    },
    {
        "text": "to prove that A\nplus B caused C.",
        "start": 202.91,
        "duration": 3.11
    },
    {
        "text": "But A and B are\njust simultaneous.",
        "start": 206.02,
        "duration": 2.68
    },
    {
        "text": "They see what\nthey want to see.",
        "start": 208.7,
        "duration": 2.083
    },
    {
        "text": "First, you mandate vaccines.",
        "start": 210.783,
        "duration": 1.667
    },
    {
        "text": "Next, you’re making all\nthe choices for my family.",
        "start": 212.45,
        "duration": 2.85
    },
    {
        "text": "Take that \"slippery\nslope\" argument far enough",
        "start": 215.3,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "and I’ll have a comeback.",
        "start": 217.5,
        "duration": 1.153
    },
    {
        "text": "So you think it’s\nhealthy to pump",
        "start": 218.653,
        "duration": 1.417
    },
    {
        "text": "kids' bodies full of toxins?",
        "start": 220.07,
        "duration": 1.59
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m going to buy that\nstraw man a drink.",
        "start": 221.66,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m sorry, there’s no way\nI’m vaccinating my children.",
        "start": 223.64,
        "duration": 3.9
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, it’s happening.",
        "start": 227.54,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "I’m really contracted, Polio.",
        "start": 229.86,
        "duration": 2.495
    },
    {
        "text": "I knew you could do it.",
        "start": 232.355,
        "duration": 1.71
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, goodbye, Polio.",
        "start": 234.065,
        "duration": 1.591
    },
    {
        "text": "Enjoy it while\nyou can, Measles.",
        "start": 235.656,
        "duration": 1.894
    },
    {
        "text": "After a few outbreaks,\nthey’ll try vaccines again.",
        "start": 237.55,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "[choir sings]",
        "start": 240.37,
        "duration": 3.05
    }
]